    "updated_at": "2016-08-22T16:13:09Z",
    "body": "Ah I just came across https://github.com/electron/electron/issues/1334, which gives a lot of context on this.\n\nThe original reason for creating this PR still applies though:\n\n> hard or nearly impossible to find any documentation or examples on how to create/simulate a local shortcut\n\nIs using [Menu items with Accelerators](http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/menu/) the preferred method of creating \"local\" shortcuts?\n"
