    "created_at": "2016-08-22T16:33:36Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-22T16:33:36Z",
    "body": "If `Menu.buildFromTemplate(template)` from the following code is similar to my commit to accomplish the same task, it isn't documented.\n\n``` js\nMenu.buildFromTemplate([\n    {\n        'label': 'Rename',\n        'accelerator': 'F2',\n        'click': () => {\n            console.log('F2 is pressed')\n        }\n    }\n])\n```\n"
