    "updated_at": "2016-08-23T07:54:34Z",
    "body": "Our documentation has actually covered everything needed for creating local shortcuts, with code examples, but users may not easily find the right page if they never did GUI programming before, since you have to associate shortcuts with menus. We can probably add a new tutorial for it.\n\nI'm closing this PR now.\n\n> Is using Menu items with Accelerators the preferred method of creating \"local\" shortcuts?\n\nYeah.\n"
